metadata.title: Denver Dining Set of 4 Natural Rattan Wicker Side Chairs with Cream Cushions and Dining Round Table Glass Top, White Wash
features: LOUNGE SET: If you love the taste of the tropics in the interior, this interior will delight you. A beautiful chairs and interestingly crafted Round Table well with the unique atmosphere of any interior.

PIECE SET: Includes Pelangi Dining Round Table and 4 Denver chairs. Dimensions of one Chair: 23" D x 18" W x 36" H. Seat Depth: 17" D; Dimensions of Cushion: 1.7"H x 17"D; Weight of chair: 8 pounds. Dimensions of Table: 35"D x 35"W x 31.5"H; Weight of Table: 22 pounds.
ASSEMBLY REQUIRED: Each chair is fully assembled; Table has easy-to-follow assembly instructions.

BUY WITH CREDENCE: The quality and beauty of our products began from our passion and attention to details. Having any issues with your order? Please feel free to contact us and we will do our best to satisfy your needs. We guarantee – all questions will be solved very quickly.
description: Denver 5-piece Dining set creates a comfortable atmosphere for everything from simple home breakfast to big gatherings. This cozy and casual dining set combines graceful legs and vintage chair backs with a round lovely tabletop and seating. Create a warm, comfortable breakfast nook or enclosed patio dining area with this incredible furniture! Set includes Dining table and 4 side chairs. Why is it so unique? Firstly, all products of this set are made from natural rattan, class A – ECO-friendly material, which comes to us from Indonesia. Secondly, this furniture will bring both comfort and style to your place. A wonderfully sized seat and a pleasant traditional style make Denver one of our best-selling products. The quality and beauty of our rattan products began from our passion and attention to details. That’s why it is an excellent decor addition to any place of your home. If you want to make your space cozy and beautiful – our family-owned company is here for you. Have any issues with your order?
